        "content": "<p>PiotrSikora requested <a href=\"https://github.com/orgs/bytecodealliance/teams/wasmtime-default-reviewers\">wasmtime-default-reviewers</a> for a review on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12719\">PR #12719</a>.</p>",
